claim.claim-text:
1. A method comprising: 
providing to a player access to an amount, 
wherein the amount comprises a plurality of portions, and wherein at least one of the portions is associated with a respective expiration period; 

determining a current time; 
determining an end time of a first expiration period that is one of the expiration periods; 
determining a first portion that is one of the plurality of portions and that is associated with the first expiration period; and 
decreasing the first portion by a predetermined decrease amount if the current time is past the end time, such that the player no longer has access to the decrease amount for purposes of gambling.

24. A method comprising: 
providing a player access to an amount, 
wherein the amount comprises a plurality of portions, and 
wherein each of the portions is associated with a respective expiration period; 

determining a current time; 
determining an end time of one of the expiration periods and the portion associated with the expiration period; 
adjusting the portion associated with the expiration period from a first value to a second value if the current time is within a predetermined time of the end time.

33. A method comprising: 
associating an amount of a first currency with an account identifier, 
wherein the amount comprises a plurality of portions of the first currency, each portion being associated with a respective expiration period, and 
wherein each portion of the first currency is usable to fund gambling activity of a player; 

determining a current time; 
determining an end time of a first portion of the plurality of portions; 
determining that the current time is within a predetermined time of the end time; and 
converting the first portion to a second currency.
